    "当前授权为只读（d1.read），写入语句会被 Cloudflare 拒绝": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Authorization is read-only (d1.read). Write statements will be rejected by Cloudflare."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "現在の認可は読み取り専用（d1.read）です。書き込み文は Cloudflare に拒否されます"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "目前授權為唯讀（d1.read），寫入語句會被 Cloudflare 拒絕"
